trans-unit.source: Implements the basic functionality that can be used to design value editors.
These editors can, in turn, provide a user interface for representing and editing the values of objects of the supported data types.
Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.ObjectSelectorEditor"></xref> class.
Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.ObjectSelectorEditor"></xref> class.
The specified sub-object selector value.
Represents the current value of <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.ObjectSelectorEditor"></xref>.
Edits the value of the specified object using the editor style indicated by <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.ObjectSelectorEditor.GetEditStyle*"></xref>.
A service provider is provided so that the editor can obtain any required services.
An <xref href="System.ComponentModel.ITypeDescriptorContext"></xref> that can be used to gain additional context information.
An <xref href="System.IServiceProvider"></xref> that this editor can use to obtain services.
The object to edit.
The new value of the object.
If the value of the object has not changed, the method should return the same object it was passed.
Determines whether the specified <xref href="System.Object"></xref> is equal to the current <xref href="System.Object"></xref>.
The <xref href="System.Object"></xref> to compare with the current <xref href="System.Object"></xref>.
`true` if the specified <xref href="System.Object"></xref> is equal to the current <xref href="System.Object"></xref>; otherwise, `false`.
Fills a hierarchical collection of labeled items, with each item represented by a <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.TreeNode"></xref>.
A hierarchical collection of labeled items.
The context information for a component.
The <xref href="System.IServiceProvider.GetService(System.Type)"></xref> method of this interface that obtains the object that provides the service.
Gets the editor style used by the <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.ObjectSelectorEditor.EditValue*"></xref> method.
An <xref href="System.ComponentModel.ITypeDescriptorContext"></xref> that can be used to gain additional context information.
A <xref href="System.Drawing.Design.UITypeEditorEditStyle"></xref> value that indicates the style of editor used by <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.ObjectSelectorEditor.EditValue*"></xref>.
Represents the previous value of <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.ObjectSelectorEditor"></xref>.
Sets the current <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.ObjectSelectorEditor"></xref> to the specified value.
The specified value.
Controls whether or not the nodes within the hierarchical collection of labeled items are accessible.
